{"tid":2115717,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【台劇】愛殺17 - 2007年懸疑驚悚神作","createTime":"2020-07-19T17:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T16:10:43.000Z","uid":24163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6321eb8febaaf27a5de2b9c4e03cec82a94191c2","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">《愛殺17》</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGNTWHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGNTWHv.jpg&h=69b3f11d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（英語：Bump off Lover），是一部驚悚推理台灣偶像劇，由張韶涵、楊士萱、陸廷威、張善傑主演。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">故事大綱</span></strong></span><br />\n17歲的夏天，美好的青春，毫無徵兆地剎那間結束&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n青春的17歲，因為，愛，意外出現了殺機，在17歲的夏天，在剎那間告別&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n徐宜真，一個無憂無慮的青春少女，當雙胞胎妹妹宜靜意外死亡後，她試着在真愛的撫慰下走出傷痛...卻無意中發覺妹妹的早逝其實只是某些血色真相的冰山一角...<br />\n<br />\n鄒克強，一個改邪歸正的回頭浪子，努力想給弟弟鄒克傑跟自己一片新藍天，弟弟克傑卻突然蒙冤成為殺人犯而含冤自殺。恨之入骨的他誓言血債血還洗清冤枉；唯一能平息他胸口瘋狂怒火的人，卻是被害者的姊姊宜真...<br />\n<br />\n17歲少女徐宜靜的意外死亡，原本傷痛似乎可以由時間緩解；而當這個看似簡單的謎團逐漸被抽絲剝繭、多年謊言逐漸破滅、盤根錯節的各種真相慢慢被拼湊還原之後，眾人能接受極端殘酷的真相嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">片頭曲 張韶涵《口袋的天空》</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IDhZy6tfJGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIDhZy6tfJGY&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pgFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=653af8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IDhZy6tfJGY</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"teal\">片尾曲 張韶涵《隱形的翅膀》</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/be2wvNFTLMc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbe2wvNFTLMc&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pgFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=f2edee9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/be2wvNFTLMc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">《愛殺17 Bump off Lover》EP.1 ─張韶涵、楊士萱、陸廷威、張善傑</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hTM-UKAt3mk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhTM-UKAt3mk&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pgFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=577d8255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hTM-UKAt3mk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">爭議</span></strong></span><br />\n本劇在中視播出第一集時，因內容涉及血腥與暴力，而遭投訴「內容過於血腥暴力，會教壞小孩」；因此，中視在播第二集時，以「基於專業素養與社會良心」為由，自行刪除約40分鐘的戲。<br />\n<br />\n之後，本劇在八大綜合台播出時，國家通訊傳播委員會（NCC）對本劇處以新台幣20萬元罰鍰；理由是本劇內容涉及校園恐嚇、勒索，網絡聊天內容談到強姦、殺人、援交與自殺，恐對青少年有不良影響。該劇編劇小組成員陳昭如認為，中視的處理方式「粗暴地肢解並扭曲原創者的作品」，NCC的處理方式「實在讓我們對台灣的言論自由與創作環境感到寒心」。<br />\n<br />\n2006年7月13日，本劇劇組召開記者會，批評NCC「開倒車重現電檢制度」；江豐宏揚言，若NCC堅持罰款，他們將到NCC抗議。<br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"e5e6f60b07790e46f14312d4fdf5f35ee0633610","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">電視台自己UP返成套上Youtube</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk2gvyPpHLReH7MH6o_mBfGGbaedeJnwq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLk2gvyPpHLReH7MH6o_mBfGGbaedeJnwq&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pgFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=138564bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk2gvyPpHLReH7MH6o_mBfGGbaedeJnwq</a></p>"},{"pid":"611f07bde7f9d84550924dbf8400fb76c68ca9c9","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbae7fcd6607b2268cd22e8bb81fa3982e992b1","tid":2115717,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f06283bde711144d939686bee394a973313d762","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcbae7fcd6607b2268cd22e8bb81fa3982e992b1","tid":2115717,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"居然有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52055517335b8ac7963ddbeb743ae5d85d83d86d","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137f23b19853696df8f7c474fa9857b78bd81778","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3900296ed98645a60df34c3618a04ee9a00a02","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290357507051bcf629893bef1fb25feb6b027951","tid":2115717,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}